\int_\Omega XdP=\lim_k\int_\Omega X_k dP=\lim_k\sum_n 2^{-n}\int_\Omega X_kdP_n=\sum_n 2^{-n}\lim_k\int_\Omega X_kdP_n=\\ =\sum_n 2^{-n}\int_\Omega XdP_n
